pr_title: [NEW] Add fastlane to android module and configure CI
pr_body:
@RocketChat/ReactNative

Closes #1991

- [x] Add Fastlane to the android module to automate android tasks
- [x] Update CircleCi config to use Fastlane to upload build to play console

pr_body:
- [x] Divide the current app into Play and Foss build
- [x] Remove all google/proprietary libraries from foss build
- [x] Remove all tracking, monitoring and reporting services like Bugsnag
- [x] Make play build functional
- [x]  Make foss build functional
- [x] Use white icons instead of blue one and other resources related changes for foss build
- [x] Add support to easily generate builds using the terminal.
`npm run play` for Play build
`npm run foss` for Foss build
